Architecture: x86_64
Operating System: Linux (tested on Ubuntu 22.04)
Storage: ~500 MB

=== Tool Versions ===

CBMC: 5.12 (cbmc-5.12) 64-bit x86_64 linux

GenMC: v0.9 (commit #b5e7340), built with LLVM 11.0.1

Nidhugg: 0.4 (9e86fc0e, Release), built with LLVM 11.0.1

Clang: 11.0.1 (for generating LLVM IR files used by GenMC and Nidhugg)

IRhunter (composed of two components):
  - UFO (dynamic instrumentation engine): Docker image "4ndychin/llvm-ufo" (LLVM 7.1.0 with modified ThreadSanitizer)
  - reorder-main (reordering prediction engine): Maven-based Java 8 project

Additional dependencies:
  - Docker (for IRhunter/UFO)
  - Maven + JDK 8 (for IRhunter reorder-main)
  - Bash (for all automation scripts)

=== Machine-Readable Dependencies ===
  - CBMC: installed via system package manager (apt)
  - GenMC: built from source (https://github.com/MPI-SWS/genmc)
  - Nidhugg: installed via system package manager
  - IRhunter/UFO: Docker image "4ndychin/llvm-ufo" (https://hub.docker.com/r/4ndychin/llvm-ufo)
  - IRhunter/reorder-main: Maven project, pom.xml included in the artifact
